      "textContent": "Doctor Kostantinos Filias, Athens General Practitioner Home About Me Resume Contact I’m available 24 HOURS MEDICAL SERVICE - KOSTANTINOS FILIAS M.D. My name is Kostantinos Filias and I’m a doctor based in Athens. I speak English, Greek, French, Swedish & German.I am available 24 hours for any medical consultations and emergencies. If you're facing any health concerns or have medical questions, feel free to reach out to us on WhatsApp. You can either call us or send a message — whichever works best for you. We recognize the importance of your health and aim to respond promptly, usually within five minutes. My doctor's offices are located in Athens, Platanias and Agia Marina. I am available 24 hours a day for any kind of medical consultations. I am specialised in Primary Care Management and competently equipped to treat chronic ailments as well as conditions that need immediate attention. MAKE APPOINTMENT NOW I can visit you at your home, hotel or office. There is no need to be registered or to have used us before. Our rapid service aims to have a doctor with you within 60 minutes. A private company in Athens and Chania, Crete is looking for doctors without a specialty (waiting for a specialty to start) or even qualified ones for the 2023 tourist season (May-October). Necessary qualifications: Very good knowledge of English language (additional language desired) Pleasant personality Driving license (desired although not necessary) Experience will be appreciated Offered: Competitive salaries Possibility to work in Chania, Athens, or both cities Send CVs to kostas102@yahoo.gr or contact 697 707 2373 In a life-threatening emergency such as sudden severe chest pain, loss of consciousness or severe bleeding - dial 166 before ringing the doctor. Connect with me Thoughts from my Twitter (function(i,s,o,g,r,a,m){i['GoogleAnalyticsObject']=r;i[r]=i[r]||function(){ (i[r].q=i[r].q||[]).push(arguments)},i[r].l=1*new Date();a=s.createElement(o), m=s.getElemen