      "textContent": "Kostantinos Filias M.D. FAMILY DOCTOR Home About Me Resume Contact About my services My medical office is located in Athens, just in front of Acropolis Museum, Kavalloti 2, 11742 Athens. I am available 24 hours a day for any kind of medical consultations. I am specialised in Primary Care Management and competently equipped to treat chronic ailments as well as conditions that need immediate attention. I can visit you at your home, hotel or my medical office located near Acropolis Museum. There is no need to be registered or to have used us before. Our rapid service aims to have a doctor with you within 60 minutes. I speak fluent English and provide quality medical care at your hotel or at your home, a place of your choosing or my medical office located near Acropolis Museum. I am fully equipped and I pride myself in catering for the needs of visitors to Greece, tourists as well as foreign workers. I will professionally respond to your problems with urgency and care. I completely understand, when at unease, even a few minutes of waiting can feel like an eternity! Personal Details Name: Kostantinos Filias Title: Doctor of Medicine Languages: English, French, Swedish, German Experience: 12 months work in Swedish Health Center in Västra Götaland Nationality: Greek Treatments Common everyday illnesses and allergies Common internal conditions ENT conditions Cuts and wounds Fractures and concussion assessment Vaccinations Pregnancy tests Laboratory health investigation referrals Chronic disease and illnesses Sexual health issues Women health problems Contact me (function(i,s,o,g,r,a,m){i['GoogleAnalyticsObject']=r;i[r]=i[r]||function(){ (i[r].q=i[r].q||[]).push(arguments)},i[r].l=1*new Date();a=s.createElement(o), m=s.getElementsByTagName(o)[0];a.async=1;a.src=g;m.parentNode.insertBefore(a,m) })(window,document,'script','//www.google-analytics.com/analytics.js','ga'); ga('create', 'UA-1099336-19', 'auto'); ga('send', 'pageview');",
